Audi May Hit 1.5 Million Annual Sales Goal, Automotive News Says

-- B y   C h r i s   R e i t e r
-- 
2011-09-03T14:28:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-03/audi-may-hit-1-5-million-annual-sales-goal-automotive-news-says.html
Volkswagen AG (VOW) ’s Audi may reach its
goal of selling 1.5 million cars a year by 2014, a year ahead of
plan, Automotive News  Europe   reported , citing an interview with
Rupert Stadler, the luxury-car brand’s chief.  Audi aims to easily achieve its goal of selling 1.2 million
vehicles this year and anticipates growth in 2012 to be fueled
by the new Q3 compact sport-utility vehicle and revamped A6
line, the newspaper reported. China will surpass Germany as
Audi’s biggest market for the first time this year, ANE said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Chris Reiter in Berlin at 
